ill begin to expire in 2029. The Com-", "bbox": [153.2, 1191.1, 1077.7, 1212.0]}, {"text": "pany also has $10.1 million of federal alternative minimum tax credit carryforwards, which do not expire. In", "bbox": [153.2, 1216.1, 1059.9, 1237.0]}, {"text": "addition, the Company has $7.6 million in charitable contribution carryforwards to offset taxable income. The", "bbox": [153.2, 1241.2, 1072.6, 1262.0]}, {"text": "Company’s charitable contribution carryforwards expire in 2018 — 2022.", "bbox": [153.2, 1266.2, 770.8, 1287.0]}, {"text": "For state taxable income, the Company has $22.1 million of state net operating loss carryforwards (net of", "bbox": [194.9, 1303.3, 1074.2, 1324.1]}, {"text": "$11.9 million of federal effects) and $1.2 million of state tax credits carryforwards (net of federal effects).", "bbox": [153.2, 1328.3, 1039.1, 1349.1]}, {"text": "Depending on the jurisdiction in which the state net operating loss was generated, the carryforwards will begin to", "bbox": [153.2, 1353.3, 1099.7, 1374.1]}, {"text": "expire between 2018 and 2032.", "bbox": [153.2, 1378.3, 414.5, 1399.1]}, {"text": "We believe it is more likely than not that the benefit from certain charitable contribution carryforwards,", "bbox": [194.9, 1415.4, 1060.5, 1436.2]}, {"text": "state net operating loss carryforwards and state credit carryforwards will not be realized. Due to the uncertainty", "bbox": [153.2, 1440.4, 1082.9, 1461.2]}, {"text": "85", "bbox": [618.1, 1490.8, 638.9, 1511.7]}]}